Speaker 1: Thank you for calling, this is John. How can I help you today?

Speaker 2: Yes, I'd like to place an order.

Speaker 1: No problem. Have you ordered with us before? Is this your first time?

Speaker 2: No, I've ordered once before.

Speaker 1: Okay, your name and zip code, please.

Speaker 2: Curtis Fairchild.

Speaker 1: What else did you want? The zip, please.

Speaker 2: Oh, 56220.

Speaker 1: Thank you, sir. Yeah, 804 Lyon Avenue North. Yes. You want to do the same thing you got the last time, 40 of the 100 milligrams?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: Last question for you, do you want me to use the same Visa card that ends in 0171?

Speaker 2: No.

Speaker 1: Yeah, use that one, yeah.

Speaker 2: Okay. What is the price now?

Speaker 1: It's the same, it was the same as before. You paid 163, it's the same price.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: You're all set though, Curtis. Your order did go through successfully, so we're all set. This will ship out in a day or two.

Speaker 2: Alrighty, thank you very much.

Speaker 1: You're welcome, sir. Enjoy your day.

Speaker 2: You too.
